I"V<p>从远程仓库克隆下来一个项目后，默认是在master分支。</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>caojinhua:git_test caojinhua$ git branch
*  master
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>查看仓库中的所有分支，使用git branch -a命令：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>caojinhua:git_test caojinhua$ git branch -a
*  master
  remotes/origin/HEAD -&gt; origin/master
  remotes/origin/master
  remotes/origin/remotebranch
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>可以看到远程仓库中有master和remotebranch两个分支。现在在本地项目中怎么样切换到remotebranch分支呢？很简单，使用git check命令，具体如下：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git checkout --track -b &lt;local branch&gt; &lt;remote&gt;/&lt;tracked branch&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>在我这里就是</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git checkout --track -b remotebranch origin/remotebranch
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>对于这个命令，有一个简化的选项：</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git checkout -t origin/remotebranch
</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="参考资料">参考资料</h3>

